commentTextItems.html: short of length ball outside off stump, cut away wide of the thirdman fielder

commentPostTextItems.html: Thats it. South Africa have won the 1st match of the 3-ODI series. Dippenaar carried his bat through the innings and has been adjudged Man-of-Match. Please join us for the next match on sunday. Cheers and Bye!

commentTextItems.html: short leg side delivery, Dippenaar works it away through mid-wicket for a couple of runs
half volley, Dippenaar tries to loft but mistimes, one bounce to mid-on fielder
full length ball on the off stump, pushed to mid-off
on the legs, glanced away to fine leg
length ball on the off stump, Pollock lofts it high and over the long-off fence
